        "header": "1.Introduction",
        "images": [
            {
                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.26562/2605.26562v1/x1.png",
                "caption": "Figure 1.Overview of the proposed TSCOMP framework. TSCOMP deconstructs existing SOTA models into a modular component pool. Through large-scale experimental analysis, TSCOMP conducts bottom-up evaluation from component-level comparisons to dimension-level and pipeline-level importance ranking. The resulting performance corpus enables automated model construction via a pre-trained meta-predictor that delivers zero-shot, data-adaptive component selection.",
                "position": 354
            }
        ]
